data.description: Welcome to 332 Poplar School Road in Centreville, MD.  This charming colonial home is nestled on a sprawling 1.5-acre lot, where classic elegance meets modern comfort. The property features a detached 2-car garage with an inviting in-law suite upstairs, boasting a full kitchen and a luxurious full bathroom.  As you enter the main house, you'll be greeted by the warmth of the well-designed space, featuring 4 spacious bedrooms. The main level boasts a convenient bedroom, perfect for guests or use as a home office. The 2.5 bathrooms in the main house are tastefully appointed, providing both functionality and style.  Step into the heart of the home, a renovated kitchen adorned with white cabinets, a large island, brand new appliances, and a built in eating space that is seamlessly opening to the family room with stunning Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) flooring, gas fireplace and built in storage shelving. The kitchen is a culinary haven, offering a perfect blend of modern convenience and classic design.  Enjoy the natural light pouring into the gorgeous sunroom, overlooking the expansive backyard. Upstairs, discover 3 additional large bedrooms, including a primary suite with a huge walk-in closet and a beautifully renovated bathroom.  Venture outside to the backyard oasis featuring a large stamped concrete patio with a built-in grill and granite tops—an entertainer's dream. Enjoy not 1 but 2 large decks off of the sunroom.  The bonus shed outback offers water, electric, options for chicken coups or any farm animals you desire!  The property also boasts  garden beds and extends beyond the fenced-in yard, providing an additional quarter of an acre (approximate) for potential expansion or recreational activities.  For added convenience, the property includes a separate shed with both electric and water connections. The detached garage not only accommodates two cars but also offers a private in-law suite, making it ideal for multigenerational living or guest accommodations.  This colonial home on 1.5 acres seamlessly combines traditional charm with modern amenities, creating a perfect retreat for comfortable living and entertaining.  Located conveniently to Rt 50, 301, 404 and all town amenities, don’t miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your new home!  (This home totals 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms when you add the in-law suite bedroom and full)bathroom
